column1:
I believe figure 1 and Figure 2 are in line with our FVE and progress upto the FVE. However, the other 2 figures considering analysis of voxels with sizes starting from 10cm and reducing feels like a big difference from the initial requirements of the project with a requirement of a map with a voxel size of 50cm. Not that it's not achievable, but this change of focus at the last moment seems new to understand and evaluate via performance metrics.
Moreover, Figure 4 seems like a new addition of analysis that wasn't previously mentioned. It certainly is a good metric to consider for the project but again, I'm not sure if changing the focus to these evaluations in the last few days instead of achieving the original requirements, that we have been working hard towards, would make sense.
